               <msContents>

                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 3ra-97rb) I-1) Maṣḥāfä
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-6rb) I-2) Introductory
                     exhortation (fols. 6rb-8va) I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... "I worship
                     Thee..." (fols. 8va-9rb) I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 90 miracles
                     (fols. 9va-77va, 82ra-89ra) I-5) ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka... "I worship Thy
                     Godhead..." (fols. 95ra-97rb) II) Taʾāmra Mikāʾel “Miracles of Michael”: 3
                     miracles (fols. 77va-79vb) III) Taʾāmra Libānos “Miracles of Libanos”: 4
                     miracles (fols. 79vb-80vb) IV) Taʾāmra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus “Miracles of Gäbrä
                     Mänfäs Qǝddus”: 2 miracles (fols. 80vb-81vb) V) Taʾāmra madḫāne ʿālam “Miracles
                     of the Saviour of the World”: 1 miracle (fols. 81vb-82ra) VI) Taʾāmra ʾIyāsus
                     “Miracles of Jesus”: 4 miracles (fols. 89ra-92ra) VII) Taʾāmra śǝllāse
                     “Miracles of the Trinity”: 3 miracles (fols. 92ra-93rb) VIII) Salām laki ḫoḫǝta
                     mǝśrāq... “Salutation to you, Threshold of the East…” (fols. 93rb-94rb) Additio
                     1.</summary>

               </msContents>


